Package: SVI
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of Stochastic Variational Inference 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zhehui Chen; Shiyang Li; Xingguo Li; Tuo Zhao
Maintainer: Shiyang Li <lsydevin@gmail.com>
Description: An implementation of Stochastic Variational Inference in R. We calculate an approximate posterior probability in two cases: 1.Latent Dirichlet Allocation and 2.Hidden Markov Model. Basically, we assume the approximate class is a mean field family. By some analysis, we get the incremental update formula. With this formula, we update the hyperparameters iteratively until they converge or the we get the maximum iteration number. 
